publisher			Iceflake Studios							
publish_time	 2016年3月14日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Premium Pool is a smooth and enjoyable way to play billiards on your computer. Practice in single player against AI and then put your skills into use in a tournament or in a wide range of different custom locations online. You can also challenge your friends locally or online. In Premium Pool everything can be customized. Gather credits from your wins and change the cue, table, cloth and balls to your liking from a vast collection of beautifully designed equipment. Who wouldn’t want to play with a royally designed table on the beach? Or use one of the uniquely designed cues in a casino? Finally personalize your character by selecting one of the awesome theme characters in the game. KEY FEATURES Online multiplayer Local multiplayer Single player Challenge your friends 8 Ball Tournament mode Super smooth controls Specially themed game rooms Customize every equipment Awesome set of avatars Chat with your competitor Option to fast forward; no need to wait all balls to settle down to continue playing Achievements and collectible cardsFuture updatesRegular content updates will be released for the game. In addition to new equipment and game locations there will be tournament mode, daily challenges and player ranking system. Also new game modes like 9 ball and snooker are in development.						
title	 Premium Pool			
